              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333] mb-1" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Shariah Compliant</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm" style="font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;">All sacrifices follow Islamic guidelines</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
